com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework

类 UIConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.UIConfig

  • public class UIConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    The UIConfig class is used to configure the look and feel of the application. Currently the ListStyle can be set to a List or Grid view for device lists, and the NavStyle can be set to Pager for a 3-pane paged view, or Drawer for a navigation drawer style app.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static class  UIConfig.ListStyle
      Enumeration of styles the list views can be shown in (all devices / device groups)
      static class  UIConfig.NavStyle
      Enumeration of navigation styles the app can be configured with

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      UIConfig.ListStyle _listStyle
      Style for all devices / device group list views
      UIConfig.NavStyle _navStyle
      Overall navigation style for the app
